Barroso Says EU Must Break Vicious Circle of Debt, Market Doubt

-- B y   J a m e s   G .   N e u g e r
-- 
2011-10-13T09:30:16Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-13/barroso-says-eu-must-break-vicious-circle-of-debt-market-doubt.html
European governments must “break
the vicious circle” of sovereign debt, weak banks and economic
sluggishness, European Commission President  Jose Barroso  said.  Barroso spoke at a press conference in Brussels today with
Danish Prime Minister Helle Thorning-Schmidt.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
